* Nouveaux langages

Working group dedicated to the study of new languages: [[http://informatique.in2p3.fr/?q=nouveaux-langages][website]]

For now, focused on the study of:

- [[http://dlang.org/][D]]: a better `C++`
- [[https://golang.org/][Go]]: a better `C`, with builtin support for concurrency

ChM investigated `D`.
SB investigated `Go`.

